msgid "The Gathering"
msgstr "聚集于此"

msgid "Scenario I: The Gathering"
msgstr "冒险I：聚集于此"

msgid "You and your partners have been investigating strange events taking place in your home city of Arkham, Massachusetts. Over the past few weeks, several townspeople have mysteriously gone missing. Recently, their corpses turned up in the woods, savaged and half-eaten. The police and newspapers have stated that wild animals are responsible, but you believe there is something else going on. You are gathered together at the lead investigator’s home to discuss these bizarre events."
msgstr "你和伙伴们正在调查发生在你家乡—马萨诸塞州阿卡姆市——的诸多怪异事件。过去几周内，数名市民神秘失踪。最近，他们遭蹂躏和啃食的尸体在树林中被陆续发现。警方和报社宣布野生动物是罪魁祸首，但你们相信其中另有内情。你们聚集在调查员队长的家中讨论这些离奇事件。"

msgid "Put the Study location into play. Set each other location aside, out of play. Each investigator begins play in the Study."
msgstr "将书房地点放置入场。将其他所有地点放在一边，位于场外。每位调查员从书房开始游戏。"

msgid "Set the Ghoul Priest and Lita Chantler cards aside, out of play."
msgstr "将食尸鬼祭司和丽塔·钱德勒卡牌放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "your house is still standing."
msgstr "你的房子幸免于难。"

msgid "the Ghoul Priest is still alive."
msgstr "食尸鬼祭司还活着。"

msgid "Lita was forced to find others to help her cause."
msgstr "丽塔不得不去向其他人求助。"

msgid "The lead investigator earns the Lita Chantler card and may include it in their deck. This card does not count toward that investigator’s deck size."
msgstr "调查员队长取得丽塔·钱德勒卡牌并可以将其加入自己的牌库。这张卡牌不计入该调查员的牌库卡牌张数。"

msgid "The lead investigator earns 1 experience, as they refused to let the night’s events destroy their life."
msgstr "调查员队长取得1点经验值，因为其拒绝让今晚的事件毁掉自己的生活。"

msgid "Each investigator earns experience equal to the Victory X value of each card in the victory display (remember to add eligible locations to the victory display)."
msgstr "每位调查员取得经验值，数量等于胜利区所有卡牌的胜利X数值之和（记得将符合条件的地点卡牌加入胜利区）。"

msgid "The lead investigator suffers 1 mental trauma from watching their home become a smoldering ruin."
msgstr "调查员队长由于目睹自己的宅邸被烧成灰烬而承受1点精神创伤。"

msgid "Each investigator who has not resigned is <b>killed</b>. If there are not enough investigators to continue the campaign, the campaign is over and the players lose. Otherwise, advance to the next scenario. (Each player whose investigator has been killed must choose a new investigator from the pool of available investigators. Refer to page 13 of the Rules Reference for the full rules on killed investigators.)"
msgstr "每位没有撤退的调查员<b>阵亡</b>。如果没有足够的调查员继续剧本，则剧本就此结束，玩家游戏失败。否则，推进至下一个冒险。（每位调查员阵亡的玩家必须从可选调查员池中选择一名新调查员。阵亡调查员的具体规则参见《规则详解》第六页。）"

msgid "Each player whose investigator has been killed must choose a new investigator from the pool of available investigators."
msgstr "每位调查员阵亡的玩家必须从可选调查员池中选择一名新调查员。"

msgid "Because the lead investigator was killed, choose an investigator to earn the Lita Chantler card. That investigator may include this card in their deck. It does not count toward that investigator’s deck size."
msgstr "如果调查员队长阵亡，选择一名调查员取得丽塔·钱德勒卡牌。该调查员可以将其加入自己牌库。这张卡牌不计入该调查员的牌库卡牌张数。"

msgid "You barely manage to escape your house with your lives. The woman from your parlor follows you out the front door, slamming it behind her. “You fools! See what you have done?” She pushes a chair in front of the door, lodging it beneath the doorknob. “We must get out of here. Come with me, and I will tell you what I know. We are the only ones who can stop the threat that lurks beneath from being unleashed throughout the city.” You’re in no state to argue. Nodding, you follow the woman as she runs from your front porch out into the rainy street, toward Rivertown."
msgstr "你们侥幸逃离宅邸，保全了性命。客厅里的女子随你们跑出了前门并重重地把门关上。“你们这些白痴!瞧见了你们做的好事？”她推来一把椅子，用它卡住了门把手。“我们必须离开这里。跟我走，我会告诉你们我知道什么。现在只有我们能阻止这蛰伏地下的威胁，不让它在城市中蔓延开来。”你无话可说，点点头随她穿过门廊，快步走上雨中的街道，朝着河岸城的方向而去。"

msgid "You nod and allow the red-haired woman to set the walls and floor of your house ablaze. The fire spreads quickly, and you run out the front door to avoid being caught in the inferno. From the sidewalk, you watch as everything you own is consumed by the flames. “Come with me,” the woman says. “You must be told of the threat that lurks below. Alone, we are surely doomed…but together, we can stop it.”"
msgstr "你点头示意，允许这红发女子点燃了你宅邸的地板与四壁。火势快速蔓延，你们从前门奔了出去，逃离了火海。你站在街边的人行道上，眼看着你所拥有的一切遭火焰吞噬殆尽。“跟我走吧，”这女子说道，“必须有人告知你们蛰伏地下的威胁。分兵作战，我们必将大难临头……只有通力合作，才能阻止这场灾难。”"

msgid "You refuse to follow the overzealous woman’s order and kick her out of your home for fear that she will set it ablaze without your permission. “Fools! You are making a grave mistake!” she warns. “You do not understand the threat that lurks below… the grave danger we are all in!” Still shaken by the night’s events, you decide to hear the woman out. Perhaps she can shed some light on these bizarre events…but she doesn’t seem to trust you very much."
msgstr "你拒绝听从这名狂热女子的号令，担心她私自纵火，便将她赶出了你的宅邸。“一群白痴!你们正在犯下致命的错误！”她警告说，“你们不理解蛰伏地下的威胁……根本不明白我们所有人都身陷何等险境!”你震惊于今晚发生的一切，决定听她说完。或许她多少能够澄清这些怪事的由来……但她似乎并不那么信任你们。"

msgid "You run to the hallway to try to find a way to escape the house, but the burning-hot barrier still blocks your path. Trapped, the horde of feral creatures that have invaded your home close in, and you have nowhere to run."
msgstr "你们奔向走廊，试图找到逃出屋子的路，但灼热的屏障仍然阻挡着你们的去路。大群入侵宅邸的凶猛怪物同样受困并朝你们包围过来，而你们无处可逃。"

msgid "Scenario I"
msgstr "冒险I"
